<h1>SL-022 Smart Classification & Tax Hints [AI]</h1>
<p class="small">Prepared for: Morshed | Project: OraBooks Lean MVP | Date: 2026-06-27</p>

<h2>Executive Summary</h2>
<p>SL-022 is implemented and operational for Lean MVP scope. Verification was completed using source evidence and fresh automated tests.</p>
<div class="box"><strong>Status:</strong> READY FOR MVP SIGN-OFF (within SL-022 scope)</div>

<h2>Implemented Scope</h2>
<ul>
<li>Core smart classification engine for expense, invoice, and journal line records.</li>
<li>Rule-first classification with AI provider path and deterministic fallback.</li>
<li>Tax hints, confidence scoring, low-confidence flag, and risk score output.</li>
<li>Apply and override governance with reason-code enforcement.</li>
<li>RBAC-aware access control for run/apply/override actions.</li>
<li>Idempotency and duplicate request protection.</li>
<li>Async queue and event-driven classification request/processing path.</li>
<li>Frontend classification panel with apply/rerun actions and user warnings.</li>
</ul>

