<p><strong>Command:</strong> D:\xampp\php\php.exe tests\vendor\phpunit\phpunit\phpunit --configuration tests\phpunit.xml tests\OraBooks_Classification_Test.php tests\OraBooks_Ai_Providers_Test.php</p>
