<h2>How to Test Manually</h2>
<ol>
<li>Run classification from Expenses page and verify suggested account/confidence/tax hint output.</li>
<li>Apply AI suggestions and confirm record updates are persisted.</li>
<li>Try override without reason (must fail), then with valid reason (must succeed).</li>
<li>Verify duplicate/idempotent request handling does not create uncontrolled duplicates.</li>
<li>Test low-confidence scenario and confirm warning/flag behavior.</li>
<li>Test provider fallback by running with and without AI credentials.</li>
</ol>

<h2>Expected Output Pattern</h2>
<ul>
<li>classification status transitions correctly (pending/processed/overridden/failed).</li>
<li>suggested_account_code and account_confidence are returned for successful runs.</li>
<li>tax_hints payload is present and usable.</li>
<li>reason text is available for explainability.</li>
<li>low_confidence is true when score is below threshold.</li>
</ul>

